OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fand bright this evening, but with the
OL,7,Fchance of a few light spots of rain,
OL,8,Fespecially across Argyll. Further
OL,9,Fshowers may develop towards dawn.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy morning with a
OL,12,Ffew light showers. Brighter and drier
OL,13,Fconditions develop in the afternoon
OL,14,Ffor Argyll, though a few showers may
OL,15,Fstill affect the Glasgow area.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
